      <title></title>
      <link href="/2023/03/02/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/02/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="数据结构"><a href="#数据结构" class="headerlink" title="数据结构"></a>数据结构</h1><h2 id="一、链表"><a href="#一、链表" class="headerlink" title="一、链表"></a>一、链表</h2><h4 id="1、定义"><a href="#1、定义" class="headerlink" title="1、定义"></a>1、定义</h4><p>线性结构的一种。</p><p>每个元素是一个独立的对象，由每个元素的引用字段串连起来。</p><h4 id="2、基本操作"><a href="#2、基本操作" class="headerlink" title="2、基本操作"></a>2、基本操作</h4><h5 id="1、单链表基本结构"><a href="#1、单链表基本结构" class="headerlink" title="1、单链表基本结构"></a>1、单链表基本结构</h5><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span> *<span class="title">next</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; Node;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>、、、</p><h5 id="2、创造一个空的头节点"><a href="#2、创造一个空的头节点" class="headerlink" title="2、创造一个空的头节点"></a>2、创造一个空的头节点</h5><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Node* <span class="title function_">create</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">Node * head = (Node*) <span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(Node));</span><br><span class="line">head-&gt;next = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> head;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、增加对象功能实现"><a href="#3、增加对象功能实现" class="headerlink" title="3、增加对象功能实现"></a>3、增加对象功能实现</h5><p>存在两种思路</p><h6 id="1、根据输入长度实现新增"><a href="#1、根据输入长度实现新增" class="headerlink" title="1、根据输入长度实现新增"></a>1、根据输入长度实现新增</h6><p>、、、 </p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Node* <span class="title function_">Add</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> length , Node* head)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">   Node * p;</span><br><span class="line">   p = head;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i =<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;length;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Node* s = (Node*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(Node));</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,&amp;s-&gt;data);</span><br><span class="line">      p-&gt;next = s;</span><br><span class="line">      s-&gt;next = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      p = s;</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">return</span> head-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="2、根据-1判断输入结束"><a href="#2、根据-1判断输入结束" class="headerlink" title="2、根据-1判断输入结束"></a>2、根据-1判断输入结束</h6><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>,&amp;i)!=<span class="number">-1</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   Node* s = (Node*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(Node));</span><br><span class="line">   s-&gt;data = i;</span><br><span class="line">   p-&gt;next = s;</span><br><span class="line">   s-&gt;next = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">   p = s;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、删除功能的实现"><a href="#3、删除功能的实现" class="headerlink" title="3、删除功能的实现"></a>3、删除功能的实现</h5><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> ListNode* <span class="title function_">removeElements</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">struct</span> ListNode* head, <span class="type">int</span> val)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">dummyHead</span> =</span> <span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="keyword">struct</span> ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">    dummyHead-&gt;next = head;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">cur</span> =</span> dummyHead;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (cur-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (cur-&gt;next-&gt;val == val) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cur-&gt;next = cur-&gt;next-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cur = cur-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">retNode</span> =</span> dummyHead-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">free</span>(dummyHead);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> retNode;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>提供一个虚拟头节点，进行删除操作，可进行删除头节点操作，而不至于直接让链表置空。</p><p>原理：让目标元素的前一个元素  直接指向  目标元素的下一个元素。再释放目标空间。</p><h5 id="4、查找元素"><a href="#4、查找元素" class="headerlink" title="4、查找元素"></a>4、查找元素</h5><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ElementType <span class="title function_">FindKth</span><span class="params">( List L, <span class="type">int</span> K )</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(L==<span class="literal">NULL</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(K&lt;<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> flag = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;K;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">if</span>(L-&gt;Next==<span class="literal">NULL</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">             flag = <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">         L = L-&gt;Next;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(flag == <span class="number">-1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(flag == <span class="number">1</span> )</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> L-&gt;Data;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>、、、</p><h5 id="5、修改元素"><a href="#5、修改元素" class="headerlink" title="5、修改元素"></a>5、修改元素</h5><p>、、、</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">change</span><span class="params">(LinkList *<span class="built_in">list</span>,<span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;<span class="comment">//n为第n个节点</span></span><br><span class="line">LinkList *t = <span class="built_in">list</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (i &lt; n &amp;&amp; t != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">t = t-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">i++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (t != <span class="literal">NULL</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">puts</span>(<span class="string">&quot;输入要修改的值&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;t-&gt;score);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">puts</span>(<span class="string">&quot;节点不存在&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、字符串和数组"><a href="#二、字符串和数组" class="headerlink" title="二、字符串和数组"></a>二、字符串和数组</h2><h3 id="定义"><a href="#定义" class="headerlink" title="定义"></a>定义</h3><p>根据数组下标去对指定元素进行操作</p><h3 id="经典问题"><a href="#经典问题" class="headerlink" title="经典问题"></a>经典问题</h3><h4 id="1、最长公共前缀"><a href="#1、最长公共前缀" class="headerlink" title="1、最长公共前缀"></a>1、最长公共前缀</h4><p>思路：通过 最小长度的字符串与其他字符串进行 横向扫描 获得结果</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> * <span class="title function_">longestCommonPrefix</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span> ** strs, <span class="type">int</span> strsSize)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(strs==<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//寻找最小长度</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> min=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;strsSize;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(strs[i])&lt;<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(strs[min]))</span><br><span class="line">            min =i;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> samelength = <span class="built_in">strlen</span>(strs[min]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//横向扫描</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i =<span class="number">0</span> ;i&lt;strsSize;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(i==min)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> current =<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> j=<span class="number">0</span>;j&lt;samelength;j++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(strs[i][j]!=strs[min][j])</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            current++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//确认节点</span></span><br><span class="line">        samelength = samelength&gt;current? current:samelength;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//置空</span></span><br><span class="line">    strs[min][samelength]=<span class="string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> strs[min] ;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2、最长回文子串"><a href="#2、最长回文子串" class="headerlink" title="2、最长回文子串"></a>2、最长回文子串</h4><p>回文串定义：正读与反读一样的字符串<br>中心扩散算法流程<br>    1、遍历字符串。<br>    2、对于每个字符，判断两侧字符是否相等，若不等，停止扩散，并记录长度。<br>    3、选出长度最大的即可。<br>代码实现</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">static</span> <span class="type">int</span> n;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">getLength</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span>* <span class="built_in">string</span>,<span class="type">int</span> begin_index,<span class="type">int</span> end_index)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//在下标不越界的前提下判断头下标和尾下标所指向的字符是否相等</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (begin_index&gt;=<span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; end_index&lt;n &amp;&amp; <span class="built_in">string</span>[begin_index]==<span class="built_in">string</span>[end_index])&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        begin_index--;</span><br><span class="line">        end_index++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> end_index-begin_index<span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">getLongestPalindrome</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span>* A )</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    n=<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(A);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> max_size=<span class="number">1</span>, x_size=<span class="number">0</span>, y_size=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//x_size记录字符长度为奇数，当前字符恰好为中心字符</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//y_size记录字符长度为偶数，当前字符和下一个字符作为中心字符</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;n<span class="number">-1</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        x_size=getLength(A,i, i);</span><br><span class="line">        y_size=getLength(A, i, i+<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//将以i-th字符为中心的回文子串的长度记录在x_size中</span></span><br><span class="line">        x_size=x_size&gt;y_size?x_size:y_size;</span><br><span class="line">        max_size=max_size&gt;x_size?max_size:x_size;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> max_size;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3、-KMP算法"><a href="#3、-KMP算法" class="headerlink" title="3、 KMP算法"></a>3、 KMP算法</h4><h5 id="1、最长公共前后缀"><a href="#1、最长公共前后缀" class="headerlink" title="1、最长公共前后缀"></a>1、最长公共前后缀</h5><p>字符串 abcdab<br>前缀的集合：{a,ab,abc,abcd,abcda}<br>后缀的集合：{b,ab,dab,cdab,bcdab}<br>那么最长相等前后缀不就是ab嘛.</p><p>字符串：abcabfabcab中最长相等前后缀<br>对，就是abcab。</p><h5 id="2、next-数组"><a href="#2、next-数组" class="headerlink" title="2、next 数组"></a>2、next 数组</h5><p>每一个字符前的字符串都有最长相等前后缀，而且最长相等前后缀的长度是我们移位的关键，所以我们单独用一个next数组存储子串的最长相等前后缀的长度。而且next数组的数值只与子串本身有关。<br>所以next[i]&#x3D;j,含义是：下标为i 的字符前的字符串最长相等前后缀的长度为j。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> data[MaxSize];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> length;<span class="comment">//串长</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; SqString;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//SqString 是串的数据结构</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//typedef重命名结构体变量，可以用SqString t定义一个结构体。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">GetNext</span><span class="params">(SqString t,<span class="type">int</span> next[])</span><span class="comment">//由模式串t求出next值</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> j,k;</span><br><span class="line">j=<span class="number">0</span>;k=<span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">next[<span class="number">0</span>]=<span class="number">-1</span>;<span class="comment">//第一个字符前无字符串，给值-1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (j&lt;t.length<span class="number">-1</span>) </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//因为next数组中j最大为t.length-1,而每一步next数组赋值都是在j++之后</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//所以最后一次经过while循环时j为t.length-2</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (k==<span class="number">-1</span> || t.data[j]==t.data[k]) <span class="comment">//k为-1或比较的字符相等时</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">j++;k++;</span><br><span class="line">next[j]=k;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//对应字符匹配情况下，s与t指向同步后移</span></span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">k=next[k];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//我们现在知道next[k]的值代表的是下标为k的字符前面的字符串最长相等前后缀的长度</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//也表示该处字符不匹配时应该回溯到的字符的下标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//这个值给k后又进行while循环判断，此时t.data[k]即指最长相等前缀后一个字符**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//为什么要回退此处进行比较，我们往下接着看。其实原理和上面介绍的KMP原理差不多</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//printf(&quot;(2) k=%d\n&quot;,k);</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、-KMP算法代码"><a href="#3、-KMP算法代码" class="headerlink" title="3、 KMP算法代码"></a>3、 KMP算法代码</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">KMPIndex</span><span class="params">(SqString s,SqString t)</span>  <span class="comment">//KMP算法</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> next[MaxSize],i=<span class="number">0</span>,j=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">GetNext(t,next);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (i&lt;s.length &amp;&amp; j&lt;t.length) </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (j==<span class="number">-1</span> || s.data[i]==t.data[j]) </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">i++;j++;  <span class="comment">//i,j各增1</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> j=next[j]; <span class="comment">//i不变,j后退，现在知道为什么这样让子串回退了吧</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (j&gt;=t.length)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span>(i-t.length);  <span class="comment">//返回匹配模式串的首字符下标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span>(<span class="number">-1</span>);        <span class="comment">//返回不匹配标志</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、栈和队列"><a href="#三、栈和队列" class="headerlink" title="三、栈和队列"></a>三、栈和队列</h2><h4 id="1、队列基本理论"><a href="#1、队列基本理论" class="headerlink" title="1、队列基本理论"></a>1、队列基本理论</h4><h5 id="1、定义-1"><a href="#1、定义-1" class="headerlink" title="1、定义"></a>1、定义</h5><p>队列是一个先入先出的数据结构（先入队的先出队），插入与删除的操作称为 入队与出队。<br>新元素始终在队列的末尾，删除时，只能删除第一个元素。<br>FIFO特性（   First    in    First   out  ）</p><h5 id="2、队列的实现"><a href="#2、队列的实现" class="headerlink" title="2、队列的实现"></a>2、队列的实现</h5><p>为了实现队列，我们可以使用链表和指针进行。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">QueueNode</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">QueueNode</span>* <span class="title">next</span>;</span><span class="comment">//指针域</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="type">int</span> data;<span class="comment">//；数据域</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;QueueNode;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Queue</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">       QueueNode* phead;<span class="comment">//头指针</span></span><br><span class="line">       QueueNode* ptail;<span class="comment">//尾指针</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、-初始化操作"><a href="#3、-初始化操作" class="headerlink" title="3、 初始化操作"></a>3、 初始化操作</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">InitQueue</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//assert() 函数为C语言中断言函数，用于检查参数合法性，不合法则报告错误，并停止运行</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//使用断言来检查参数的合法性</span></span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//置空两个指针</span></span><br><span class="line">       pq-&gt;phead = pq-&gt; ptail = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="4、入队操作"><a href="#4、入队操作" class="headerlink" title="4、入队操作"></a>4、入队操作</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">QueuePush</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq , <span class="type">int</span> data)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//开辟空间接受新元素</span></span><br><span class="line">       QueueNode* newNode = (QueueNode*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span> (<span class="keyword">sizeof</span> (QueueNode));</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//判断开辟是否成功</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span>(newNode == <span class="literal">NULL</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;malloc failed\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">-1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       newNode -&gt;data =x;</span><br><span class="line">       newNode -&gt;next = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//首次添加</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span>(pq-&gt;phead==<span class="literal">NULL</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           pq-&gt;phead = pq-&gt;ptail = newNode;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//非首次添加</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           pq-&gt; ptail-&gt;next = newNode;</span><br><span class="line">           pq-&gt;ptail = newNode;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="5、判空"><a href="#5、判空" class="headerlink" title="5、判空"></a>5、判空</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">return</span> pq -&gt; phead ==<span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="6、删除（出队）"><a href="#6、删除（出队）" class="headerlink" title="6、删除（出队）"></a>6、删除（出队）</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">deleteQueue</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//为空时不能删除</span></span><br><span class="line">       assert(!isEmpty(pq));</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//只有一个节点</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span>(pq-&gt;phead-&gt;next == <span class="literal">NULL</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">free</span>(pq-&gt;phead);</span><br><span class="line">           pq-&gt;phead = pq-&gt;ptail =<span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           QueueNode* next = pq-&gt;phead -&gt; next;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">free</span>(pq-&gt;phead);</span><br><span class="line">           pq-&gt;phead = next;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="7、长度"><a href="#7、长度" class="headerlink" title="7、长度"></a>7、长度</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">Queue_length</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="type">int</span> cnt=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       QueueNode* cur = pq-&gt;phead;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">while</span>(cur)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           cnt++;</span><br><span class="line">           cur=cur-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">return</span> cnt;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="8、销毁"><a href="#8、销毁" class="headerlink" title="8、销毁"></a>8、销毁</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">QueueDestroy</span><span class="params">(Queue* pq)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       assert(pq);</span><br><span class="line">       QueueNode* cur = pq-&gt;phead;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">while</span>(cur)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           QueueNode* next = cur-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">free</span>(cur);</span><br><span class="line">           cur = next;</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       pq-&gt;phead = pq-&gt;ptail = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2、循环队列-元素个数示意图"><a href="#2、循环队列-元素个数示意图" class="headerlink" title="2、循环队列 元素个数示意图"></a>2、循环队列 元素个数示意图</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\86157\Desktop\学习\循环队列.jpg" alt="循环队列"></p><h4 id="3、栈"><a href="#3、栈" class="headerlink" title="3、栈"></a>3、栈</h4><h5 id="1、定义-2"><a href="#1、定义-2" class="headerlink" title="1、定义"></a>1、定义</h5><p>栈：一种特殊的线性表，其只允许在固定的一端插入和删除元素操作。进行数据插入和删除操作的一端称为栈顶，另一端称为栈底。<br>栈中的数据元素遵守后进先出LIFO (Last In First Out) 的原则；同时对于栈来说，一种入栈顺序对应多种出栈顺序</p><p>1️⃣ 压栈：栈的插入操作叫做进栈&#x2F;压栈&#x2F;入栈，入数据在栈顶。</p><p>2️⃣ 出栈：栈的删除操作叫做出栈。出数据也在栈顶 。</p><h5 id="2、实现"><a href="#2、实现" class="headerlink" title="2、实现"></a>2、实现</h5><p>这里对于栈的实现我们既可以选择数组也可以和选择链表两者的效率都差不多，但是还是建议使用数组</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="type">int</span> STdatatype;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Stack</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    Stdatatype* space;<span class="comment">//开辟的空间</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> top;<span class="comment">//栈顶位置</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> capacicy;<span class="comment">//容量</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;ST;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3、初始化"><a href="#3、初始化" class="headerlink" title="3、初始化"></a>3、初始化</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">StackInit</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    ps-&gt;space =<span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ps-&gt;top=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ps-&gt;capacicy =<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="4、压栈"><a href="#4、压栈" class="headerlink" title="4、压栈"></a>4、压栈</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">StackPush</span><span class="params">(ST* ps, STDatatype x)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//检查容量，满了就扩容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(ps-&gt;top == ps-&gt;capacicy)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//若是第一次开辟，开辟4个空间 ，后面开辟原容量的两倍</span></span><br><span class="line">           <span class="type">int</span> newcapacity = ps-&gt;capacity == <span class="number">0</span> ? <span class="number">4</span> : ps-&gt;capacicy *<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//第一次开辟时， realloc == malloc，后面则是扩充；</span></span><br><span class="line">       STdatatype* temp = <span class="built_in">realloc</span>(ps-&gt;space, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(STDatatype) * newcapacity);</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//检查开辟</span></span><br><span class="line">       <span class="keyword">if</span>(temp == <span class="literal">NULL</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;realloc failed\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">           <span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">-1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">       &#125;</span><br><span class="line">       </span><br><span class="line">       ps-&gt;a = temp;</span><br><span class="line">       ps-&gt;capacicy = newcapacicy;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//插入</span></span><br><span class="line">ps-&gt;a[ps-&gt;top] =x;</span><br><span class="line">ps-&gt;top ++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="5、判空-1"><a href="#5、判空-1" class="headerlink" title="5、判空"></a>5、判空</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> ps-&gt;top == <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="6、删除操作"><a href="#6、删除操作" class="headerlink" title="6、删除操作"></a>6、删除操作</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">Delete</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//保证非空</span></span><br><span class="line">    assert(!isEmpty(ps));</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    -- ps-&gt;top;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="7、长度-1"><a href="#7、长度-1" class="headerlink" title="7、长度"></a>7、长度</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">ST_Length</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> ps-&gt;top;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="8、栈顶数据"><a href="#8、栈顶数据" class="headerlink" title="8、栈顶数据"></a>8、栈顶数据</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">STDatatype <span class="title function_">StackTop</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//找栈顶的话得保证指向的空间不为空</span></span><br><span class="line">assert(!StackEmpty(ps));</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//此时的top-1就是栈顶数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> ps-&gt;a[ps-&gt;top - <span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="9、销毁"><a href="#9、销毁" class="headerlink" title="9、销毁"></a>9、销毁</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">StackDestroy</span><span class="params">(ST* ps)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    assert(ps);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(ps-&gt;a)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">free</span>(ps -&gt; a);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ps-&gt;a = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    ps-&gt;top = ps -&gt; capacicy =<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
